{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778432328603,"sessionID":"ses_1ed339b18ffe5kTmxqWqbpAn8A","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_xzbg1rA3YHwqOza6J2TbOnhr","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/references_cache/PMID_20883697.md","offset":1,"limit":200},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/references_cache/PMID_20883697.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: ---\n2: reference_id: PMID:20883697\n3: title: \"Identification of a plant gene encoding glutamate/aspartate-prephenate aminotransferase: the last homeless enzyme of aromatic amino acids biosynthesis.\"\n4: authors:\n5: - Graindorge M\n6: - Giustini C\n7: - Jacomin AC\n8: - Kraut A\n9: - Curien G\n10: - Matringe M\n11: journal: FEBS Lett\n12: year: '2010'\n13: doi: 10.1016/j.febslet.2010.09.037\n14: keywords:\n15: - \"Amino Acids, Aromatic/metabolism\"\n16: - \"Arabidopsis/cytology, enzymology, genetics\"\n17: - \"Arabidopsis Proteins/genetics, metabolism\"\n18: - \"Aspartate Aminotransferases/genetics, metabolism\"\n19: - \"Cells, Cultured\"\n20: - \"Electrophoresis, Polyacrylamide Gel\"\n21: - Glutamic Acid/metabolism\n22: - Kinetics\n23: - Mass Spectrometry\n24: - \"Recombinant Proteins/isolation & purification, metabolism\"\n25: - \"Transaminases/genetics, metabolism\"\n26: content_type: abstract_only\n27: ---\n28: \n29: # Identification of a plant gene encoding glutamate/aspartate-prephenate aminotransferase: the last homeless enzyme of aromatic amino acids biosynthesis.\n30: **Authors:** Graindorge M, Giustini C, Jacomin AC, Kraut A, Curien G, Matringe M\n31: **Journal:** FEBS Lett (2010)\n32: **DOI:** [10.1016/j.febslet.2010.09.037](https://doi.org/10.1016/j.febslet.2010.09.037)\n33: \n34: ## Content\n35: \n36: 1. FEBS Lett. 2010 Oct 22;584(20):4357-60. doi: 10.1016/j.febslet.2010.09.037.\n37: Epub  2010 Sep 29.\n38: \n39: Identification of a plant gene encoding glutamate/aspartate-prephenate \n40: aminotransferase: the last homeless enzyme of aromatic amino acids biosynthesis.\n41: \n42: Graindorge M(1), Giustini C, Jacomin AC, Kraut A, Curien G, Matringe M.\n43: \n44: Author information:\n45: (1)Université Grenoble 1, Grenoble, France.\n46: \n47: In all organisms synthesising phenylalanine and/or tyrosine via arogenate, a \n48: prephenate aminotransferase is required for the transamination of prephenate \n49: into arogenate. The identity of the gene encoding this enzyme in the organisms \n50: where this activity occurs is still unknown. Glutamate/aspartate-prephenate \n51: aminotransferase (PAT) is thus the last homeless enzyme in the aromatic amino \n52: acids pathway. We report on the purification, mass spectrometry identification \n53: and biochemical characterization of Arabidopsis thaliana prephenate \n54: aminotransferase. Our data revealed that this activity is housed by the \n55: prokaryotic-type plastidic aspartate aminotransferase (At2g22250). This \n56: represents the first identification of a gene encoding PAT.\n57: \n58: Copyright © 2010 Federation of European Biochemical Societies. Published by \n59: Elsevier B.V. All rights reserved.\n60: \n61: DOI: 10.1016/j.febslet.2010.09.037\n62: PMID: 20883697 [Indexed for MEDLINE]\n\n(End of file - total 62 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"---\nreference_id: PMID:20883697\ntitle: \"Identification of a plant gene encoding glutamate/aspartate-prephenate aminotransferase: the last homeless enzyme of aromatic amino acids biosynthesis.\"\nauthors:\n- Graindorge M\n- Giustini C\n- Jacomin AC\n- Kraut A\n- Curien G\n- Matringe M\njournal: FEBS Lett\nyear: '2010'\ndoi: 10.1016/j.febslet.2010.09.037\nkeywords:\n- \"Amino Acids, Aromatic/metabolism\"\n- \"Arabidopsis/cytology, enzymology, genetics\"\n- \"Arabidopsis Proteins/genetics, metabolism\"\n- \"Aspartate Aminotransferases/genetics, metabolism\"\n- \"Cells, Cultured\"\n- \"Electrophoresis, Polyacrylamide Gel\"","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"references_cach